The Genius被懷疑有抄襲日本電視劇[[Liar_Game|Liar Game]]之嫌，<ref>{{cite news |title='더 지니어스', 예능에 버무려진 '처세술'의 향연 |trans_title='The Genius', 只是一個單純的'處世術' |author=Park So-Youn 記者 |language=ko |date=2013-05-15 |publisher=OhmyStar |url=http://star.ohmynews.com/NWS_Web/OhmyStar/at_pg.aspx?CNTN_CD=A0001865409 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305105056/http://star.ohmynews.com/NWS_Web/OhmyStar/at_pg.aspx?CNTN_CD=A0001865409 |archivedate=2016-03-05 |accessdate=2015-09-04 }}</ref>The Genius的製作方在未經Liar Game的任何許可或版權的情況下擅自引用了Liar Game的概念，形式，演戲及遊戲規則等，<ref name="TV REPORT">{{cite news|title='더 지니어스', 日 '라이어게임' 표절 의혹…tvN "참고했지만 달라"|trans_title='The Genius', 日本Liar Game抄襲指控…tvN "只是參考，並未抄襲"|language=ko|author=Yisuah 記者|date=2013-04-27|publisher=TV Report|url=http://www.tvreport.co.kr/?c=news&m=newsview&idx=339189|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927130604/http://www.tvreport.co.kr/?c=news&m=newsview&idx=339189|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然The Genius方有關人物主張「只是參考，並未抄襲」，<ref>{{cite news|title=日本のドラマ「ライアーゲーム」を盗作？人気バラエティのプロデューサーが釈明“参考にしたが…”|language=ja|author=チョン・ウォン 記者|date=2014-09-26|publisher=Kstyle|url=http://news.kstyle.com/article.ksn?articleNo=2004514|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305222144/http://news.kstyle.com/article.ksn?articleNo=2004514|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TV REPORT"/>但對抄襲遊戲規則一事卻未作解釋，Liar Game的粉絲們要求The Genius做出真正的解釋和道歉<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://namu.wiki/w/%EB%8D%94%20%EC%A7%80%EB%8B%88%EC%96%B4%EC%8A%A4/%ED%91%9C%EC%A0%88%20%EB%85%BC%EB%9E%80 |title=더 지니어스/표절 논란 |accessdate=2015-09-03 |date=2013-12-16 |trans_title=The Genius/抄袭风波 |format=Wiki |publisher=Namu Wiki |language=ko |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150904130626/https://namu.wiki/w/%EB%8D%94%20%EC%A7%80%EB%8B%88%EC%96%B4%EC%8A%A4/%ED%91%9C%EC%A0%88%20%EB%85%BC%EB%9E%80 |archivedate=2015-09-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWWZ_SUkT-k|title=더 지니어스 고발 영상 - 라이어 게임 표절|date=2015-06-24|format=YouTube|publisher=Henry Miller|language=ko|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314141752/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWWZ_SUkT-k|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C-fFTNWsbBQ|title=The Genius Zombie Game, Liar Game Angels and Demons Game Plagiarism (EN, JP, KR 3 sub)|date=2015-05-16|format=YouTube|publisher=Henry Miller|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310090534/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C-fFTNWsbBQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

不巧的是，2014年tvN將播放[[詐欺遊戲_(韓國電視劇)|Liar Game的改版劇]]，也就是說，tvN演了一場同時播放抄襲作品和改版作品的絕妙的戲。<ref name="MBN">{{cite news|title=‘더지니어스3’, ‘라이어게임’과 불편하지 않은 동거 가능할까|author=Ansung-Un 記者|language=ko|date=2014-09-06|publisher=MBN Star|url=http://star.mbn.co.kr/view.php?no=1176620&year=2014|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926050405/http://star.mbn.co.kr/view.php?no=1176620&year=2014|dead-url=yes}}</ref>另外，Liar Game的版權自2011年以來由其製作方Apollo Pictures單獨持有，<ref>{{cite news|title=믿고 보는 케이블 드라마, 줄줄이 새 시즌 준비…볼거리 풍성|author=Hongseyoung 記者|language=ko|date=2014-11-28|publisher=Sports Donga|url=http://sports.donga.com/3/all/20141128/68239906/2|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008010122/http://sports.donga.com/3/all/20141128/68239906/2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=‘라이어 게임’ PD “원작 판권, 제작사가 모두 보유한 상태”|author=Hongseyoung 記者|language=ko|date=2014-11-28|publisher=Sports Donga|url=http://sports.donga.com/3/all/20141125/68156203/2|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007234001/http://sports.donga.com/3/all/20141125/68156203/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>tvN和The Genius的製作公司至2015年現在為止並未得到任何與Liar Game有關的版權或許可<ref name="MBN"/><ref>{{cite news|title=표절이라는 건지 아니라는 건지|author=Lee Seung Hwan TV Columnist|language=ko|date=2015-06-19|publisher=한겨례|url=http://www.hani.co.kr/arti/culture/entertainment/696777.html|accessdate=2015-09-04|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924165341/http://www.hani.co.kr/arti/culture/entertainment/696777.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

